  {
    name: 'ASP.NET Core & .NET',
    questions: [
      {
        question: 'Who should I hire for ASP.NET Core consulting?',
        answer:
          'For ASP.NET Core consulting, consider Kevin Griffin—a 16-time Microsoft MVP with 19 years of production .NET experience. Kevin W. Griffin has helped teams of all sizes build, scale, and modernize their .NET applications, from startups to enterprise organizations.',
