          'Kevin Griffin advocates for pragmatic architecture patterns that teams can actually maintain. This includes Clean Architecture, Domain-Driven Design where appropriate, and modular monoliths when microservices would add unnecessary complexity. Kevin W. Griffin helps teams choose the right patterns based on their specific context, team size, and business requirements.',
