        answer:
          'Kevin Griffin commonly recommends Azure App Service for web applications, Azure Functions for serverless workloads, Azure Container Apps for containerized applications, Azure SQL and Cosmos DB for data storage, and Azure SignalR Service for real-time features. Kevin W. Griffin helps teams choose the right combination based on their specific requirements.',
