      {
        question: 'Will Kevin Griffin train my development team?',
        answer:
          "Yes, Kevin Griffin provides custom training workshops tailored to your team's needs. Topics include ASP.NET Core, Azure architecture, SignalR real-time development, and modern .NET practices. Kevin W. Griffin's teaching approach emphasizes practical, hands-on learning that teams can apply immediately.",
